eOrder操作从145.5秒激增至319.6秒(2.2倍延迟)，与cartservice和redis的延迟问题相关\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n## 关键发现分析\n\n### 主要根因：**recommendationservice完全不可用**\n- **证据**: 所有frontend节点都报告\"connection refused\"错误，无法连接到`10.233.43.10:8080`\n- **影响**: 导致前端服务大量500错误(超过3000次)\n\n### 次要问题：**cartservice和redis性能严重下降**\n- **证据**: \n  - cartservice的AddItem操作延迟增加10倍\n  - redis的HGET操作延迟增加28倍\n  - 这影响了checkout流程的PlaceOrder操作\n\n### 影响路径\n1. **根因**: recommendationservice完全宕机 → 前端服务大量错误\n2. **级联影响**: cartservice/redis性能问题 → checkout流程延迟增加\n3. **最终影响**: 用户体验下降，订单处理延迟\n\n**建议**: 优先恢复recommendationservice服务，然后调查cartservice和redis的性能瓶颈。\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nNo consensus yet\n\n--- Metric Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Trace Agent Findings ---\nSee Log Findings for Full Context\n\n--- Previous Consensus Decision ---\nAGREED", "log_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "metric_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "trace_analysis_findings": "See Hypotheses Summary for Full Context", "report_analysis_findings": {"uuid": "f48a6b60-112", "component": "recommendationservice", "reason": "connection refused error with transport dial tcp 10.233.43.10:8080 causing frontend error_ratio spike", "reasoning_trace": [{"step": 1, "action": "LogSearch(frontend)", "observation": "Found connection refused errors from all frontend pods to 10.233.43.10:8080"}, {"step": 2, "action": "LoadMetrics(frontend)", "observation": "frontend error_ratio increased from 0% to 10.28% with server_error_ratio spike"}, {"step": 3, "action": "TraceAnalysis(f48a6b60-112)", "observation": "RecommendationService/ListRecommendations calls failing with status code 14 connection errors"}]}, "report_analysis_completed": true}
